title: Rep. Stephanie Murphy, Impeachment
itunes:title: Rep. Stephanie Murphy, Impeachment
description:
Guests: Rick Davis, Bloomberg contributor, Partner at Stone Court Capital,and former campaign manager for John McCain's 2008 presidential campaign, Emily Tisch Sussman, Democratic Strategist, and Host of "Your Political Playlist Podcast," and Rep. Stephanie Murphy, a Florida democrat representing the 7th congressional district.
